folder: St. Nicholas Avenue & 155th Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
St. Nicholas Avenue (old Knightsbridge Road) at N.E. corner     of 155th Street, showing houses numbered 905 to 916 adjoining vacant corner. One of these, 906, antedates 1865; the others were built shortly after.
Early in the 1920's, 906 and 908, the nearest to the camera, will be torn down, and the block rebuilt to the corner.
About 1912.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
